          "date": "2013-04-03 22:42:18.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-1199 build: Rename ldiskfs rpm ldiskfs",
        "message": "LU-1199 build: Rename ldiskfs rpm ldiskfs\n\nThe ldiskfs rpm package has been named lustre-ldiskfs for some\ntime, which seems to imply that it is created as part of the\nlustre.spec file.  In reality, it was designed to be its own\nstand-alone package with its own build system and separate spec\nfile.  This naming is less surprising.\n\nChange-Id: I4dec26d15989fa644df155657c6bea7fdde2f12a\nSigned-off-by: Christopher J. Morrone <morrone2@llnl.gov>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
